/*
For the Google groups integration:


1) Use the instructions here to create a service account and get your customer number: https://developers.google.com/workspace/guides/create-credentials#create_a_service_account
2) Add the json file for the service account to the secrets folder.
3) Update your .env file with the following:
- GOOGLE_CUSTOMER_ID=Cxxxxxxxx
- GOOGLE_AUTH_JSON=secret/json_file_name
- GOOGLE_AUTH_WITH=email address of the account the service account will use for delegation (user@domain.com)
4) Follow the instructions here to give the service account domain delegation to be able to administer the groups: https://developers.google.com/identity/protocols/oauth2/service-account#delegatingauthority

*/
